Class Records

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Records
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Created by Canopy on 2017-01-20. This class for records. It implements Serializable so getSerializableExtra can be used by activities to retrieve objects. It includes setters and getters for encapsulation.
